originalText.text: I received the best support for managing my short-term rental with Usquire. They were fast, reliable and easy to communicate with. I manage over 7 properties on Airbnb aside from my main job, making coordinating, cleaning and hosting a big blur for me. A friend recommended Usquire after hiring them for mostly cleaning services.  I spoke with them about my issue with time management, hosting. I got a package deal that covered all of my needs within my budget. I absolutely recommend them if you're looking to profit from your short-term bookings like Airbnb or if you just need a reliable cleaning service. Seriously go USQUIRE!
